OL,3,CAmanda Abbington: Other Strictly
OL,4,Ccontestants 'scared' to speak out
OL,6,FBut interviews invariably centre
OL,7,Faround the storm that has enveloped
OL,8,Fher since she left Strictly Come
OL,9,FDancing, amid claims of abuse and
OL,10,Fcruelty from her dancing partner
OL,11,FGiovanni Pernice - claims he has
OL,12,Fstrenuously denied.
OL,14,FAbbington tells me that other previous
OL,15,Fcontestants have met with her to share
OL,16,Ftheir concerns, but it is she who has
OL,17,Fgone public, speaking on camera about
OL,18,Fwhat she says happened to her during
OL,19,Fthe last series of the hit show, which
OL,20,Fshe left last year after five weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
