OL,6,FIt is because, she says, others are
OL,7,Ffrightened of the consequences of
OL,8,Fspeaking out. It is this fact that she
OL,9,Fwants to change, to create a safe
OL,10,Fspace for contestants in the future to
OL,11,Fvoice any worries they have.
OL,13,FAbbington first voiced her concerns
OL,14,Fafter three days, she tells me.
OL,16,FCameras were installed in the
OL,17,Frehearsal rooms after this. In all,
OL,18,Fthere are 50 hours of footage that she
OL,19,Fand her lawyer would like to see, but
OL,20,Fshe says she has been denied access to
OL,21,Fit.
