OL,6,FWhat will it show, I ask?
OL,7,F"Everything," she replies. She tells
OL,8,Fme the footage was reviewed at the end
OL,9,Fof each week, with producers
OL,10,Fexpressing shock only for it all to
OL,11,Fresume the next week, until she left.
OL,13,FAbbington won't go into details of the
OL,14,Fexact allegations she is making
OL,15,Fagainst Pernice while the BBC
OL,16,Finvestigation is continuing.
