OL,6,FIn a statement, Pernice's spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are cooperating fully with
OL,8,Fthe BBC's review process.
OL,10,F"All parties have been asked to
OL,11,Frespect this process and to not speak
OL,12,Fto the media before it concludes.
OL,14,F"As part of the evidence-led review,
OL,15,Fthe BBC has shared the allegations and
OL,16,Fthere are none, nor any evidence, that
OL,17,Fresemble Amanda Abbington's numerous
OL,18,Fand variable allegations.
