OL,6,F"The BBC has shared the allegations
OL,7,Fand there are none, nor any evidence,
OL,8,Fthat resemble Amanda Abbington's
OL,9,Fnumerous and variable allegations.
OL,11,F"Giovanni refutes any claim of
OL,12,Fthreatening or abusive behaviour, and
OL,13,Fhaving provided the BBC with his
OL,14,Fevidence, is confident that the review
OL,15,Fwill prove this.
OL,17,F"Giovanni has not seen or blocked the
OL,18,Fvideo footage which belongs to the
OL,19,FBBC."
