OL,6,F"Our processes on Strictly Come
OL,7,FDancing are updated every year, they
OL,8,Fare kept under constant review and
OL,9,Flast week we announced additional
OL,10,Fsteps to further strengthen welfare
OL,11,Fand support on the show."
OL,13,FThe organisation has already announced
OL,14,Fnew welfare and support for
OL,15,Fcontestants on the hit show.
OL,17,FWould you ever do a show like this
OL,18,Fagain I ask - "No, never," she gasps.
OL,19,F"I'll stick to the acting."
